        Get component from a given setting object.
        Parameters:
        setting - the setting object.
        animation - the animation supplier
        adder - the component adder for any pop-ups
        theme - the theme to be used
        colorLevel - the panel nesting level, in case the component is a container (e.g. color components)
        isContainer - whether this component is a title bar
